headline: WWE® AND SEAGRAM'S ESCAPES SPIKED™ LAUNCH FIRST-EVER CO-BRANDED PRODUCT
summary: WWE, part of TKO Group Holdings (NYSE: TKO), and Seagram's Escapes, known for great tasting flavored malt beverages, today announced a new, multi-year partnership highlighted by the launch of their first-ever co-branded product of Seagram's Escapes Spiked. This marks WWE's first-ever licensed ready-to-drink product.
